title: #92Noon LIVE at TCO! Twins/Wobby/Zimmer/Thielen/Diggs/Birk
description: #92Noon is back inside the TCO Performance Center! Nordo has seen the football light, the surging Minnesota Twins are talked about, Wobby makes his regular appearance. Zimmer's weekly presser plus a bonus presser with Stefon Diggs, Adam Thielen joins in studio and the Birk Bit closes out a jam packed show!
